section.featuresSlider
  .featuresSlider__content
    h2.subPage__title.featuresSlider__title Key Features
    .featuresSlider__btns
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_left
        | left
        +icon('arrow')
      button.featuresSlider-btn.featuresSlider-btn_right
        | Right
        +icon('arrow')
  .swiper.featuresSlider-swiper
    ul.featuresSlider-list.swiper-wrapper
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Built-in  Routing based on different triggers
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Collect digital assets and auto-route them to treasury, ops wallets, or partners based on configurable rules (bps, asset, chain, wallet tags).
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Batch Payment Processing
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Send tokens to thousands of wallets automatically on schedule or based on custom triggers. Perfect for reward distributions, team payments, contributor compensation, and large-scale token operations.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Cross-Chain Settlement
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Abstract bridging and settlement. Execute operations across networks with a single unified interface. Ditto handles the complexity of multi-chain coordination.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Decentralized executors with Guarantees
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Globally distributed operators, slashing, and restaked security reduce single-point failures. Each run is timestamped, MEV-aware, and audit-ready.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title AA-Native &amp; Dev-Friendly
          span.featuresSlider-list__text Account Abstraction sessions and paymasters for gas-free experiences. Ship via SDKs, white-label widgets, or API; integrate approvals and webhooks in minutes.
      li.featuresSlider-list__item.swiper-slide
        .featuresSlider-list__content
          span.featuresSlider-list__title Non-Custodial Architecture
          span.featuresSlider-list__text All payment operations work in a fully non-custodial manner. Funds remain under your control with flexible integration options, including Ditto account abstraction wallets or your existing SAFE vaults.
